{"tid":1666946,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆點解去清真寺道歉?","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:04:57.000Z","uid":275086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46c0a30443c8d2d64d47d6b940dc2db9ebefb063","tid":1666946,"uid":275086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得柒婆親身去道歉，唔係因為射中清真寺，而係射中前香港印度協會主席Mohan Chugani呀。<br />\n<br />\n\u0016//尖沙嘴清真寺昨遭警方水炮車的藍色水柱射中致受染污，特首林鄭月娥及警務處長盧偉聰今日親身前往清真寺解釋。但有市民批評，距離清真寺不足一百米、有逾百年歷史的香港二級歷史建築「聖安德烈堂」昨日其實亦「遇襲」，拱門及牆壁的石磚同樣遭警方水炮染藍，但同為天主教徒的特首林鄭月娥以及香港警方卻未有任何表示，更遑論是道歉，故質疑政府及警方是「大細超」，亦不尊重歷史古蹟。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKpoym2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKpoym2.jpg&h=b05c8ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191021/60178273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60178273&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERU8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=7c30167e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60178273&h=b1694c9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191021/60178273</a>"},{"pid":"92476b5fac3d16e6ea6ae9650ca916a45f0b82c1","tid":1666946,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa02e6ad75f6e5f0e06daf768c8e8fea87a4b58","tid":1666946,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"兩回事嚟 <br />\n佢兩個都有道歉<br />\n但毛漢話唔接受"},{"pid":"1607b4e39dad95ae67d49257b8639e119a